{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "採用だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're hired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 1.9963265419006349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "お前には、麻奈専属のアシスタントマネージャーに\nなってもらう。二人でデビュー目指して頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want you to become Mana's exclusive assistant manager.\nLet's work together to aim for her debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2,
      "endTime": 10.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "endTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……俺がいきなりマネージャーですか？\nアルバイトですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Am I suddenly working as a manager?\nI thought this was a part-time job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "endTime": 16.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "話した通り、ウチは立ち上げたばかりだからな\nバイトだろうと、ばりばり働いてもらうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I said‚ our agency is just starting out.\nWhether it's a part-time job or not‚ you're going to work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 24.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.033333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "やったね、{user}くん！\nううん、マネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay‚ {user}!\nNope‚ you're my manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.033333333333335,
      "endTime": 29.099999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "今日から私のために\n馬車馬のように働いてね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting today‚ work like a workhorse\nfor my sake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3,
      "endTime": 33.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……せめて人間扱いはして欲しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…At least treat me like a human being.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 36.199999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj004.m4a",
      "text": "では、早速都内のレッスンスタジオに行ってくれ\nボイトレとダンスだ。先方にはもう連絡してある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ please go to a rehearsal studio in Tokyo right away.\nYou have voice and dance training. I've already informed them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "endTime": 45.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、行こっか、{user}くん\n……じゃなくて、マネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we go‚ {user}?\n…I mean‚ Manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 49.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、引っ張るなよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don't pull me like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 52.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 633.3333333333328,
          "startTime": 50.666666666666664
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1033.3333333333385,
          "startTime": 51.06666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj005.m4a",
      "text": "……はは、元気だな、若者は\n結構なことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haha‚ you've got some energy‚ young man.\nThat's quite something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 58.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 58.86666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.56666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん、今、麻奈ちゃんと男の人が\n一緒に出て行きましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mr. Saegusa‚ Mana-san and a man left\ntogether just now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 64.93333333333332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 59.56666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj006.m4a",
      "text": "あいつは麻奈のクラスメイトだ\n今日から麻奈のアシスタントマネージャーになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He's Mana's classmate.\nHe became Mana's assistant manager from today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 72.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしては随分若いですね\n私よりは、年上に見えますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ he looks pretty young.\nHe seems older than me though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "endTime": 78.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj007.m4a",
      "text": "学校で麻奈の隣の席に座っているそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He sits in the seat next to Mana at school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3,
      "endTime": 82.46553287506103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、高校生なんですか？\n高校生のマネージャーなんて聞いたことないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ is he a high school student?\nI've never heard of a high school student being a manager before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 88.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saegusa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-shj008.m4a",
      "text": "俺ももちろんフォローはするさ\nまあ、どのみち、男手は欲しかったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll support him‚ of course.\nAnyway‚ we needed a man helping hand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 95.43333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "はあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 97.16353743871053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_lesson_evening",
      "startTime": 98.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "dancea",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-dancea.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-dancea001.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬さん、腹式呼吸習ったことあるの？\n凄いわ、もう出来てるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nagase‚ have you ever learned diaphragmatic breathing?\nIt's amazing. You've already got this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 107.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　そうですか？\nやった、褒められたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Is that so?\nYay‚ I got praised!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 112.20717753001622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺に言わなくていいから\n今は練習に集中して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to tell me.\nJust focus on practicing now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4,
      "endTime": 116.49999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "dancea",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-dancea.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-dancea002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、1、2、3、4\nうん、長瀬さん、ボックスステップは完璧ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ 1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4.\nYes‚ Nagase‚ your box step is perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7,
      "endTime": 124.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 700.0000000000028,
          "startTime": 117.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "以前、動画で観て覚えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I learned it by watching videos before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 126.80387748082478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "dancea",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-dancea.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_03-dancea003.m4a",
      "text": "なら、サイドの動きも入れましょう\n私についてきて。右、後ろ、左、後ろ",
      "translations": {
